  <summary date="2025-06-09T18:39:43Z" status="Introduced in House">Buffalo Soldiers Congressional Gold Medal Act of 2025

This bill provides for a Congressional Gold Medal to be awarded to the Buffalo Soldier regiments (six all-Black cavalry and infantry regiments authorized by Congress in 1866 to serve in the Armed Forces) in recognition of their vital service to the United States.</summary>
